00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:26,380
without passing through any transition at all,

657
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:28,980
without passing through any discontinuity at all.

658
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:32,000
That's called going around the critical point.

659
00:24:33,380 --> 00:24:35,420
And some of you who are familiar

660
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:38,180
