662
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:44,520
without passing through a sudden abrupt change,

663
00:24:44,660 --> 00:24:47,400
by going around the critical point.

664
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:49,660
So that corresponds to going around the critical point.

665
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:51,840
I'm pointing these things out just to show you that

